Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎究竟他妈怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些是赫克托的黑暗生物吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are these Hector's night creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放马过来吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come on then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们被袭击了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎黑暗生物来袭 有成百上千个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}By night creatures. Hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那 ‎只有一个人能做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, there's only one person that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们要带你离开这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪儿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一个安全的地方 我不能让你身处险境\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Somewhere safe. I can't have you in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎抱歉 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sorry, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我真的很抱歉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I honestly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但这才是我要去的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But this is right where I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎丹塔利翁普雷西迪奥\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dantalion Presidio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托 你在做什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是巫师 记得吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm a wizard, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不值得信任\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not to be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个把戏非常聪明 ‎但我们没时间玩了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That was a very clever trick that we don't have time for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎时间永远都不够用 对吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Never enough time in the end, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我希望时间够用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But time enough, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没时间多说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎计算结果看起来是正确的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The calculations look correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但你要用第二个门标来控制流向\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but you want a second gating mark to control the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有 别相信瓦尼 祝你好运\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And don't trust Varney. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我失陪了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我现在要去杀人了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have to go and get killed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚究竟是怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎镜子吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我从你关在地牢里的‎疯子吸血鬼巫师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I got it from one of the mad vampire wizards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那里弄来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you keep in the dungeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们真的很容易收买\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're really very easily bribed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道我的意思 我是问 你刚刚做了什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, and you know I mean, what did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那个啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh. That.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一直在和其他学者商量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I've been conferring
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎想办法让德古拉起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with fellow scholars on a way to bring Dracula back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎既然我一开始就杀了他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It seemed only fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这样做似乎才公平\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}since I got him killed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我这个月在这里设下了几个陷阱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I laid a few traps in here during the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为你永远不会知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because, well, you never know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么时候需要结实的笼子 对吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when you're going to need a good cage, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你一定是疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一直都很疯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在这感觉不像疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This doesn't feel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许我已经清醒了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe I've gone sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后就成了这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放过她吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她难道不是卡米拉的执政理事会成员吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this not one of Carmilla's ruling council?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你是来杀我的 那就杀我吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you're here to kill me, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但是放过她 她不是这里的威胁\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But leave her alone. She is not the threat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你是威胁吗 ‎赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you the threat, Hector?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉才是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎艾萨克 我已经想办法让德古拉起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Isaac, I've taken steps to return Dracula to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我已经采取行动 弥补发生的一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've done my part to atone for all that has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我说完了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你报仇吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没有敌意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hold no malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不是来杀你的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你和我 赫克托 我们一直是孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You and I, Hector, we have been children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只有孩子才复仇\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Revenge is for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有责任成长起来 你不觉得吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is our duty to grow up, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我试着成长过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've tried to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们该找到自己的路了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is time to find our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我想你帮个忙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I will ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这地方有很多你制造的黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This place has many of your night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎命令他们退后\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Command them to stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我做不到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 命令和控制权经我的手交给丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. Command and control flows through me to Lenore here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和她的朋友们了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and to her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等等\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我趁没人注意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I used debris from broken hammers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎用破锤子的碎片做了这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to make this while nobody was looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎几周以来 我在城堡上下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been putting down fenceposts for an escape channel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎设置了逃生通道的围栏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}all through the castle for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个通道能带我到哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How far will this channel take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一直到卡米拉的房间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All the way up to Carmilla's chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只能假设有一天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I had to assume I might be running
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我可能会从城堡顶上逃走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}from the top of the castle one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎把你的念力放在上面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Place your intent upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎命令是"巴尔之始"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The command is "Ba'al Initium."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你还挺忙的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我需要谋划出路\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I needed a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉实际上有意统治全世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla intends to actually, literally rule the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我怀疑全世界发现 ‎这对他们没什么好处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I suspect the world would find that bad for its health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她待在我身边很安全\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This one stays safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎另一方面 ‎卡米拉也许应该见见你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla, on the other hand, should probably meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我同意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I tend to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但就算这个装置起作用了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But even if this device works,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也要花时间打败‎你为她制造的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}it would take time to fight through the creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you've made for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能借你的刀吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can I borrow your knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我刚刚切断了卡米拉‎对黑暗生物的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just cut off Carmilla's command and control
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥和控制\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}over the night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让他们更容易被杀死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Makes them easier to pick off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赶快去做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎女士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他要去杀了卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's going to murder Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但不会杀你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也不杀我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or me, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真是出人意料\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道接下来该怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't really know what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎围在我身边\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Surround me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎巴尔之始\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ba'al Initium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎干得漂亮 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well done, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是艾萨克吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is that Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉的城堡里最无趣的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The least interesting man in Dracula's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你好 卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello, Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吃屎去吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Eat shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是因为德古拉吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this about Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你想杀人 赫克托在楼下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector's downstairs, if you want someone to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我跟赫克托谈过了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've spoken to Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 原来如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人类要团结在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The humans are sticking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道你生出了更大的野心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I understand you have developed some more ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,除了野心 ‎我什么都没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm nothing but ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是女王\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个世界属于我...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This world belongs to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为你们这样的人 ‎从来不知道该怎么应对世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because the likes of you never knew what to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不确定这就是拥有世界的意义\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not sure that is the point of having a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是什么德鲁伊扯谈\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What kind of druid bollocks is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是你摧毁了德古拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}An opinion I came to after wandering the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他的大军和城堡之后\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}following your destruction of Dracula,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我周游世界得出的结论\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}his army and his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我从没碰过他的城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I never touched his fucking castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以你亲自来施第里尔杀我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So you've personally come to Styria to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎‎我想 没有你 世界会更美好 没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think the world would be a better place without you, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不值得被信任\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我总是害怕‎你和你的野心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I would always fear you and your ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 我非常害怕 我必须杀了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, yes, I'm very much afraid I have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看看你们所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look at you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还不够强大 杀不了我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're not big enough to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们什么都不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们不配让我流血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You don't deserve my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等你死了下地狱以后\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And when you die and go to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会‎拿着锋利的木桩...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll be there waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里等你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with a sharp bloody stick
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,用最大的决心搞清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and the determination to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否能死两次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if you can die twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:19:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是施第里尔的卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am Carmilla of Styria,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去死吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我赢了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你也感觉到了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did you feel that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉刚刚死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们该怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎城堡里到处都是黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The castle is swarming with night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托的怪物吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector's monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除非他能在几天内制造几百个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not unless he could make hundreds in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们入侵...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}An invasion, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我们的卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they killed our Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得丽诺尔…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you think Lenore...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是卡米拉死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If Carmilla is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那丽诺尔肯定早死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}then Lenore certainly died first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们要不要夺回城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Should we retake the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们不知道会遇到什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We don't know what we'd be riding into.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道是否有足够的士兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know if I have enough soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以试试\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们应该去吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎结束了 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有 ‎我们还没结束\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. Not for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在想什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎西部的城市卖给我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The cities of the west sold me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很多士兵 ‎在我们离开期间守护施第里尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}quite a lot of soldiers to guard Styria in our absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想他们全都死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I presume they're all dead up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在一个新的乱世里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In a newly uncertain world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那些城市不会挑剔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}those cities won't be fussy about where they take
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从哪里找到临时援军\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}temporary reinforcements from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是简单的交易\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's simple commerce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有什么计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有计划怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What if there isn't a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果只有你和我怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What if it's just you and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想我可能不介意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I might be all right with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉有计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla had plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼总是有计划的 对吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampires always have plans, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许我们的天性就是过度扩张\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe it's just in our nature to overreach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一次抓住太多东西 ‎打算吸所有人的血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}grasp at too much at once, try to drink everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许这就是为什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe that's why, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎最后我们赢了所有战役 ‎却总是输掉战争\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we win all the battles but always lose the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎斯崔格...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Striga...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你和我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们又不需要别的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not like we ever really needed anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你和我 永远在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You and I forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们向西进发\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We ride west!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的吸血鬼朋友呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where's your vampire friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这座建筑有间地下室 她现在待在下面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This structure has a basement. She's down there for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的手怎么样了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How is your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我可能再也不能弹奏管风琴了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I may never play the pipe organ again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你弹过吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did you ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有 但我可能想弹\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, but I might have wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们现在要去帮助德古拉伯爵归来吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do we now ride to aid the return of Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-不  ‎-什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- No. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但是…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我已经为此努力好几个星期了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been working towards this for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那还用说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你感到内疚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You feel guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想得到救赎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You want redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想弥补我的错误\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to mend my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.86,0:24:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你为这些错误受苦了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The mistakes you have suffered for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.15,0:24:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎话虽如此 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That said, Hector,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.86,0:24:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在这些事件中没有任何责任\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you had no agency in those events.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.45,0:24:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你被操纵了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You were manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你被人当成了利用的工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You were used as a tool for leverage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.86,0:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那些人才真正需要\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}by those who are truly responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对‎德古拉的死亡负责\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for the end of Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.07,0:24:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你相信吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.11,0:24:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我花了很多时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have had a lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.36,0:24:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来整理和思考这一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to put it all together and think it all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道吗 我甚至和其他人谈过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you know, I've even been talking to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.24,0:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真正的活人吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Actual living people?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.48,0:25:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎差不多吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.28,0:25:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你变了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎希望如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.49,0:25:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我相信你也变了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I believe you have as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让他安息吧 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let him sleep, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都受到了人类世界的亏待\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We were both mistreated by the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.65,0:25:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都崇拜德古拉伯爵的智慧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We were both admirers of Dracula's intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都在他身上看到了比我们更强大的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We both saw something bigger than ourselves in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.59,0:25:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都想看到世界受到惩罚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We both wanted to see the world punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以做得更多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can do more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉伯爵应该安息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula earned his rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.34,0:25:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以向前走 也应该向前走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can and should move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想要什么 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do you want, Hector?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想单独待着…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to be left alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和丽诺尔一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.96,0:26:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想读书 做事 思考\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to read, and make things, and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.69,0:26:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我现在真正想要的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's all I really want now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.69,0:26:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你会如愿以偿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then you shall have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想要什么 艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do you want, Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.31,0:26:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我最近开始考虑未来...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have recently begun to consider the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.89,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这对我来说很新鲜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}which has been a novelty for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.22,0:26:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为我从没有真正想过 我会有未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because I never really thought I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.97,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们就是这样利用了我们 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is how they get us, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.80,0:26:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们说服我们没有未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They convince us that there is no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在只有一种永恒...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's only an eternal now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.26,0:27:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们能做的最好的事就是活到黎明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and the best we can do is survive until dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.10,0:27:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后再来一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then do it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.72,0:27:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那可不是生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's no way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.64,0:27:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让人惊讶的是 我发现...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I've discovered, to some surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.10,0:27:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我对生活很感兴趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that I am interested in living.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.76,0:27:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我对建立生活方式很感兴趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am interested in building a way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.51,0:27:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想从这里开始\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I think I will start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.14,0:27:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我开始思考 ‎德古拉伯爵也许\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have come to wonder that perhaps Dracula
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.85,0:27:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,过得并不好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}did not run things well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎甚至在他妻子死前\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Even before his wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.01,0:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他生活在孤独长夜里 从没有未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He lived in one long night, and never the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.14,0:27:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得也许他应该安息…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think perhaps he earned his rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:28:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们不应该打扰他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and that we should not disturb it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.26,0:28:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎相反 我会在旧骷髅上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will instead build something new
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.60,0:28:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,建立新世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}on all these old bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可以让人们为未来而活的世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Something where people can live for a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.18,0:28:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要开始生活了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm going to live.
